{"tid":2069002,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"堅持抗爭不後悔被捕  王宗堯：黎明前係好X黑暗","createTime":"2020-06-18T05:46:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T22:45:12.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0a55fbf37e3f28acbc79605046855f2eae1a8b5a","tid":2069002,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T05:46:56.000Z","msg":"堅持抗爭不後悔被捕 <br />\n王宗堯：黎明前係好X黑暗<br />\nJun 17, 2020<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/YMfSQqex_sc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FYMfSQqex_sc&d=j4yDeGq49jMu68ZzGhcJHugMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=79fada60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/YMfSQqex_sc</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蘋果動新聞 HK Apple Daily<br />\n1.67M subscribers<br />\n<br />\n【娛樂人物】去年6.12，大批市民因反對修訂逃犯條例於凌晨聚集立法會及政府總部，王宗堯親到金鐘現場支援，7月1日示威者佔領立法會，事後王宗堯被指涉嫌參與佔領而被警方拘捕，前日律政司更加控他暴動罪，最高刑期增至10年。面臨有機會面對牢獄之災，王宗堯直言「都知道荒謬，會有最壞嘅打算。」日前於深水埗支持民主女神像展覽的他，更於連儂牆貼上「香港人不死」memo，並勉勵手足：「黎明前嗰刻真係好X黑，但黎明應該好快到。」<br />\n撰文：比華利<br />\n攝影：仇志德<br />\n<br />\n蘋果日報 ： <a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com&d=j4yDeGq49jMu68ZzGhcJHugMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=1b6e0090\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com&h=bbd68420\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com</a><br />\n<br />\n即 like 蘋果 fb  ： <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia&d=j4yDeGq49jMu68ZzGhcJHugMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=50609718\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia</a><br />\n<br />\niPhone App ： <a href=\"http://bit.ly/AppleDailyApp-iPhone\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FAppleDailyApp-iPhone&d=j4yDeGq49jMu68ZzGhcJHugMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=83fd9058\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/AppleDailyApp-iPhone</a><br />\n<br />\nAndroid App ： 